# statistics.sakmath - Sakum symbolic mathematics: Statistics
# domain=Mathematics/Statistics  format=sakmath

# --- Descriptive ---
माध्य μ = (1/n) Σ x_i
प्रसरण σ^2 = (1/n) Σ (x_i - μ)^2
मानक_विचलन σ = √(σ^2)

# --- Distributions ---
सामान्य f(x) = (1/(σ√2π)) e^{-(x-μ)^2/(2σ^2)}
द्विपद P(k) = C(n,k) p^k (1-p)^{n-k}

# --- Inference ---
विश्वास_�ंतराल μ ± z·(σ/√n)

# self-test hook
परीक्षा {
  लेख "statistics.sakmath loaded"
  लेख(लेटेक्स(माध्य μ = (1/n) Σ x_i))
}
